Emmanuelle Devos https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emmanuelle_Devos 0 Emmanuelle Devos (born 10 May 1964) is a French actress. She is the daughter of actress Marie Henriau. She won the César Award for Best Actress in 2002 for her performance in Sur mes lèvres, directed by Jacques Audiard. She has also been nominated further three times for the award. She was a member of the Jury for the Main Competition section at the 2012 Cannes Film Festival. Emmanuelle_Devos ( born 10_May_1964 ) is a_French_actress .
